<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q12_v12" title="Q12_v12" adaptive="false" time-dependent="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una campaña de recaudación de fondos se lleva el siguiente registro:</p>
    <p>
      Meta de dinero: $8 000 (
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      pesos)<br />
      Monto recaudado hasta ahora: $7 000 (
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      pesos)<br /><br />
      ¿Qué porcentaje de la meta ya se ha recaudado?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        
        12,5%
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <strong>12,5%</strong> corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,125</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero aquí se ha recaudado <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,875</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>87,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        
        14,3%
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <strong>14,3%</strong> no coincide con la razón entre lo recaudado y la meta. El cálculo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,875</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y al convertir a porcentaje se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,875</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>87,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, no <strong>14,3%</strong>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        
        70%
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si fuera <strong>70%</strong>, entonces lo recaudado sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,70</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5&#160;600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Pero el monto recaudado es <strong>7 000</strong> pesos. El cálculo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,875</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>87,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        87,5%
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El porcentaje recaudado se calcula con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,875</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,875</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>87,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, ya se ha recaudado <strong>87,5%</strong> de la meta.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la parte y el total</strong></p>
            <p>La meta total es de 8 000 pesos y el monto recaudado hasta ahora es de 7 000 pesos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Formar la razón entre lo recaudado y la meta</strong></p>
            <p>El porcentaje se obtiene dividiendo la parte por el total:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>7&#160;000</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>8&#160;000</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir la fracción a decimal</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,875</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Convertir el decimal a porcentaje</strong></p>
            <p>Para pasar de decimal a porcentaje, se multiplica por 100:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>0,875</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>87,5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Ya se ha recaudado <strong>87,5%</strong> de la meta, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la <strong>D</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>